<h2 id="bug-fixes-11">Bug fixes (11)</h2>

<ul>
  <li>On the packaged installation the â€œSend iCalendarâ€ button in meetings
caused an error.</li>
  <li>The breadcrumb was partially hidden when following the link to
activities
(<a href="https://community.openproject.com/projects/openproject/work_packages/24477/activity">#24477</a>).</li>
  <li>The work package toolbar menu was not visible on small screens
(<a href="https://community.openproject.com/projects/openproject/work_packages/24679/activity">#24679</a>).</li>
  <li><span class="explanatory-dictionary-highlight" data-definition="explanatory-dictionary-definition-7">Work
