  <li>Duplicated wiki pages could not be removed
(<a href="https://community.openproject.com/projects/openproject/work_packages/24582/activity">#24582</a>).</li>
  <li>Error shown when editing a user and using a reverse proxy server
(<a href="https://community.openproject.com/projects/openproject/work_packages/24622/activity">#24622</a>).</li>
  <li>Inactive users were shown on the homescreen of the OpenProject
